    <h1 class="heading">Backgrounds with UI Gradients</h1>
    
    <p class="info">
      With the help of <strong>UI Gradients</strong>, you can get beautiful gradient backgrounds with a variety of colors. 
      <br>
      Click on the button to UI Gradients and press the shift key to get access to all kinds of different gradients that you can apply to your own site.
    </p>
    
    <div style="padding:20px;">
      <a class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" style="padding:10px;" href="https://uigradients.com/#CoolSky" target="_blank">
