    <p class="info">
      Once you have found the right color, press the enter/return key to have the CSS code pop up on your screen.
    </p>
    <img src="/images/ui3.jpeg" alt="UI Gradients 3" style="width:700px;height:400px;padding-left:20px"><br><br>
    <p class="info">
      Now all you have to do is copy and paste that code into your CSS file. Notice that we put it under body because we want it to apply to the entire webpage.
